These are Puzzles for 2x2 Level 4

.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-4-1::.
The people have 2 different hobbies: card-games, collecting
City: london, san-francisco
1. the person traveling to london is in an even position##4
2. the person traveling to san-francisco is the person who's hobby is collecting##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |     1      |     2      |
| Hobby   | collecting | card-games |
| City     | san-francisco    | london   |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-4-2::.
City: prague, marseilles
The people prefer 2 different types of sport: sailing, weightlifting
1. the person who's sport is sailing is in an odd position##4
2. the person traveling to marseilles is on the left of the person traveling to prague##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |    1     |       2       |
| City   | marseilles | prague        |
| Sport      | sailing  | weightlifting |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-4-3::.
The people prefer 2 different music-genres: ambient, house
2 different games are played: billiard, whist
1. the person playing billiard is in an odd position##4
2. the fan of house is on the left of the fan of ambient##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |    2    |
| Music-Genre   | house    | ambient |
| Game   | billiard | whist |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-4-4::.
There are 2 different favourite beverages: 7up, lemonade
The people's birthday is in 2 different months: may, april
1. the person drinking lemonade is on the right of the person drinking 7up##1
2. the person who's birthday is in april is in an even position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|            |    1     |    2     |
| Beverage   | 7up      | lemonade |
| Birthday       | may | april    |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-4-5::.
The people have 2 different jobs:  fisherman, social-worker
The people have 2 different hobbies: singing, drawing
1. the person who's hobby is singing is in an even position##4
2. the social-worker is on the right of the fisherman##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |       2       |
| Job           | fisherman | social-worker |
| Hobby   | drawing    | singing         |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-4-6::.
The people prefer 2 different types of sport: climbing, rugby
2 different pets are kept: lizard, pony
1. the owner of the lizard is in an even position##4
2. the owner of the pony is on the left of the person who's sport is climbing##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |   1   |     2     |
| Sport       | rugby | climbing  |
| Pet   | pony  | lizard |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-4-7::.
