.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-4-10::.
There 2 different types of food: blueberry, corn
The people prefer 2 different types of sport: rugby, volleyball
1. the person who's sport is volleyball is the person eating corn##1
2. the person who's sport is rugby is in an even position##4

.:: Answer ::.
