.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-4-11::.
The people perfer 2 different movie-genres: horror, sports
The people prefer 2 different types of sport: skiing, volleyball
1. the person watching sports movies is in an odd position##4
2. the person who's sport is skiing is on the left or right of the person watching horror movies##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |     2      |
| Movie-Genre   | sports | horror   |
| Sport         | skiing | volleyball |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-4-12::.
