.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-4-19::.
The people use 2 different means of transport: bike, motorbike
The people prefer 2 different types of sport: rugby, water-polo
1. the person driving the motorbike is on the right of the person driving the bike##1
2. the person who's sport is water-polo is in an even position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|         |   1   |     2      |
| Transport    | bike  | motorbike    |
| Sport   | rugby | water-polo |

